&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leads weekly consultation sessions focused on student goals and documentation compliance&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt; with assigned clinician(s). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
